## Pricing Competitive Analysis

### Price Distribution

**Premium Tier ($40K+):**

- 11% of market
- Focuses on strategy, transformation, executive coaching
- Average engagement length: 6-12 months
- Margin profile: 40-60%

**Mid-Tier ($15-40K):**

- 46% of market
- Blended services (strategy + training)
- Average engagement length: 3-6 months
- Margin profile: 25-40%

**Value Tier ($5-15K):**

- 30% of market
- Training, workshops, certification
- Average engagement length: 1-3 months
- Margin profile: 15-30%

**Ultra-Low Tier (<$5K):**

- 13% of market
- Online learning, self-service platforms
- Continuous access model
- Margin profile: 10-20%

