### Differentiation Opportunities

**Lowest Competition:**

1. **Measurement & Analytics Platforms** (3% of market)
- High barrier to entry (tech + expertise)
- High margin potential (50-70%)
- Strong market demand
1. **Industry-Specific DEI Programs** (15% of market)
- Vertical specialization (tech, healthcare, finance, etc.)
- 35% pricing premium possible
- Growing demand
1. **Technology-Enabled Learning** (8% of market)
- AI-powered assessment and personalization
- Scalability advantage
- Emerging market

