## Market Share Projections (5-Year)

### Current State (2026)

- Fragmented market (80+ competitors)
- No single player >5% market share
- Average firm: 12-15 employees

### Projected Shift (2031)

- **Consolidation:** 40-50% reduction in total competitors
- **Top 5 Players:** 25-30% combined market share
- **Specialization:** Clear vertical leaders emerging
- **Platformization:** 3-5 tech-enabled leaders capturing premium pricing

